{"tid":1843229,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(求中醫撚）預防武漢肺炎中醫藥方，求分析","createTime":"2020-01-26T06:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T10:35:51.000Z","uid":163841,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d0010e17407ececac5a725013b0ac120497f42cc","tid":1843229,"uid":163841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:11:53.000Z","msg":"有內地中醫貼左條方，唔駛負皮住，求中醫撚分析下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n温邪上受，首先犯肺，故而会出现，严重的急性呼吸道综合症。过去的MERS和SARS，正是此类。板蓝根和奥斯它伟都不能有效预防和治疗。在此开个有效预防的方子给大家。清瘟救苦方：  生黄芪15g、北沙参12g、银翘10g、玄参10g、神曲10g、生甘草6g。  可以抓7-10付。隔1-2天喝一付预防即可。<br />\n<br />\n自己執藥煲黎試下先，<br />\n藥方應該冇毒食唔死人掛，好過第日要食愛滋藥先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d1027676a635822f57c42be889a9f50ec3c10f","tid":1843229,"uid":75232,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母而家病毒丫，仲固本培完？<br />\n撚夠時間丫？"},{"pid":"b1be01c7fd08f977c7c79af009714c01496cac59","tid":1843229,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3d1027676a635822f57c42be889a9f50ec3c10f","tid":1843229,"uid":75232,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母而家病毒丫，仲固本培完？<br />\n撚夠時間丫？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:20:37.000Z","msg":"你係連登其中一個我關注嘅人<br />\n可摸耳幫我簽個名"},{"pid":"f64f51c3bb5108232f3573366684626498263c8f","tid":1843229,"uid":168158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:23:59.000Z","msg":"幫手推下，未試過就唔信，試過就當真，我信中醫既。不過唔多識睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f2103657c8e2c1f6b9b61b549301d593f7089a","tid":1843229,"uid":112845,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c64155e1c42049c98f6fc9df6104224b5843f52","tid":1843229,"uid":163841,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"41f2103657c8e2c1f6b9b61b5